cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.CY 

The paper discusses privacy threats against genomic data sharing beacons, which involves both security and privacy concerns. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves data management and analysis, which suggests cs.DB (Databases) as the second likely category. Machine learning techniques are used to identify and analyze the vulnerability, which suggests cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the third likely category. The paper also involves information retrieval and search, which suggests cs.SI (Information Retrieval) as the fourth likely category. Finally, the paper involves computational biology and bioinformatics, which suggests cs.CY (Computational Biology and Bioinformatics) as the fifth likely category.
